illions of students.</p>\n<p>While not without limitations, especially regarding personalized guidance and user engagement, Khan Academy’s platform stands out for its accessibility, adaptive learning features, and comprehensive feedback mechanisms. For many students, particularly those from underserved communities, these practice tests represent an invaluable opportunity to prepare effectively without financial strain.</p>\n<p>In an increasingly competitive admissions environment, tools like Khan Academy’s SAT practice tests exemplify how technology and thoughtful partnerships can broaden educational access and empower students to achieve their academic goals.</p>",
